nftMetadata.description: The Jin Chan is a mythical creature that is said to appear during the full moon, near houses or businesses that will soon receive good news. Most of the time, the nature of this good news is understood to be wealth-related.  According to feng shui beliefs, Jin Chan helps attract and protect wealth, and guards against bad luck.
